data.description: Welcome your friends and family into this beautiful home, in a well established, friendly neighborhood close to shopping, eating, and more! LARGE eat-in kitchen with island, granite tops, and SS appliances. Formal dining, formal living room that can also be used as a bonus/hobby room/playroom/office, etc! Split bedrooms on the upper level of the home with lots of space and storage. Look out the kitchen windows to the huge backyard, extra parking on the side of the home (even for an RV) and great storage. Large laundry room you can even put a desk/office area in. Don't miss this great home!
